Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:35.34,CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\b0\bord0\1c&H686760&\fax0.1\fay0.1\frz42.65\pos(771.9,560.98)}不要喝最右邊水龍頭的水，據說裡面爬過蟑螂。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:35.34,CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\b0\bord0\1c&H686760&\fax0.1\fay0.1\frz42.65\pos(909.15,662.3)}車站前的友誼商店有賣室內鞋。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:42.97,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\move(950.4,226.4,950,310,959,1919)\an8\fs48\b0\bord0\1c&H464545&)\frz300.1}謝謝。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:55.32,CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\b0\bord0\1c&H61605E&\fax0.1\fay0.1\frz42.65\pos(926.29,486.3)\fad(300,0)}我也是轉校生，一年前轉來的。
